narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would not recommend this class to a fellow student because it does not teach students how to connect their knowledge and solve actual problems.
If you're taking it after calc in high school, there are some different topics and it doesn't come as easily as it may have before. Put the most time of any class into this one
A necessary pre req but needs more impovment to help those who really need to impove their maths.
